      "metadata": {
        "title": "Mingle2 - Dating & Meet People",
        "subtitle": "Match, Chat & Make New Friends",
        "promotional_text": null,
        "description": "Discover Mingle2 \u2013 Your Gateway to Meaningful Connections!!!\n\nDive into the vibrant community of Mingle2, where making meaningful connections is fun and effortless. Whether you're looking to find new friends, engage in lively chats, or start a romantic relationship, Mingle2 has you covered. Our app and website are among the largest free online dating services, tailored to suit everyone's needs. Enjoy a seamless experience with features designed to help you connect with like-minded individuals and build lasting relationships. Discover why millions are choosing Mingle2 and start your journey today!\n\nWHY JOIN MINGLE2?\n\u22c5 Instant Matches: Receive daily match recommendations tailored to you.\n\u22c5 Global Search: Connect and chat with people from around the world.\n\u22c5 Nearby Connections: Easily find and chat with people in your local area.\n\u22c5 Unlimited Likes: Send as many likes as possible to maximize your chances.\n\u22c5 Free Premium Features: Access features like sending direct chats without waiting for a match, with daily limits to prevent misuse.\n\u22c5 Social Features: Enjoy Nudges, view Who's Online, and many other features to help form meaningful relationships.\n\u22c5 Privacy Protection: Your personal information is secure, with easy account deletion and blocking options.\n\u22c5 Photo Verification: Enhance authenticity by verifying your account with a photo pose, helping to limit fake profiles and improve trust.\n\nHOW TO USE MINGLE2?\n\u22c5 Sign Up: Create your profile in just 30 seconds!\n\u22c5 Search Locally or Globally: Find someone special in your area or anywhere in the world.\n\u22c5 Start Chatting: Begin conversations with people you like.\n\u22c5 Filter Preferences: View members that match your criteria.\n\u22c5 Online Users: Chat with online users worldwide.\n\u22c5 Mutual Match: Play and meet someone wonderful.\n\u22c5 Other Features: Explore constantly improving features designed to help you find meaningful relationships, regardless of your location or relationship goals.\n\nSECURITY & PRIVACY\n\u22c5 Scam Fight System: Our advanced system combines automatic tools, human oversight, and AI for 24/7 monitoring and continuous improvement.\n\u22c5 Dating Safety Hub: Safety tips to protect yourself, avoid scams, and safeguard personal information are displayed on every chat screen.\n\u22c5 24/7 Customer Support: Chat directly with our support team anytime.\n\u22c5 Report Suspicious Profiles: Use the \"report\" feature for automated and human review.\n\u22c5 Absolutely NO Seeding Profiles: We do not create fake profiles or associate with scammers. Although high-tech scammers may generate fake profiles, we monitor and remove them swiftly, constantly improving our system to combat them.\n\nFREE vs PAID FEATURES\nWith Mingle2, you can enjoy premium features for free with daily limits to prevent misuse. Send direct chats without needing mutual matches, and utilize features like Rewind and Nudge. Additionally, you can send unlimited likes, maximizing your chances of finding a compatible partner. On the free plan, ads are shown to help fund the product's maintenance and development. You don't need to pay to enhance your search or find a meaningful relationship. However, a paid subscription is available to save you time and add convenience, offering an even smoother experience.\n\nMinglePlus Subscription:\n\u22c5 3-month subscription: $29.99\n\u22c5 6-month subscription: $47.99\n\u22c5 12-month subscription: $69.99\n\nNotice:\n\u22c5 Prices are in U.S. dollars, may vary internationally, and are subject to change. Payments will be charged to your iTunes account and automatically renew 24 hours before the current subscription period ends (3/6/12 months). You can turn off auto-renewal through your Apple device or iTunes store. If auto-renewal is turned off, your subscription will expire at the end of the current period.\n\n-------\nContact Support:\nhttps://mingle2.com/welcome/contact_us\n\nPrivacy Policy: \nhttps://mingle2.com/welcome/showPrivacy\n\nTerms of Use: \nhttps://mingle2.com/welcome/showTOS\n\nCommunity Standards:\nhttps://mingle2.com/welcome/code_of_conduct",
